    "start_date",
    "end_date",
    "price",
    "link",
    "content_url",
		"banner_type",
		"type"
)

    '{{insert_form.formData.start_date}}',
    '{{insert_form.formData.end_date}}',
    '{{insert_form.formData.price}}',

	  '{{insert_form.formData.banner_type}}',
	  '{{insert_form.formData.type}}'
);
